OL,7,FSaturday's Wales vs Scotland match saw
OL,8,Fa 35-29 victory to Gregor Townsend's
OL,9,Fside and a tenth successive Six
OL,10,FNations loss for Wales. But, whatever
OL,11,Ffans on either side might feel about
OL,12,Fthe result, the match marked a very
OL,13,Fspecial anniversary for Dai and
OL,14,FShirley Richards.
OL,16,FShirley, who is Scottish, and her
OL,17,Fhusband Dai, who is Welsh, met by
OL,18,Fchance when Dai travelled up to
OL,19,FScotland to watch Scotland v Wales in
OL,20,F1985.
