OL,7,FDai's family and friends often
OL,8,Ftraveled to watch Wales play and had
OL,9,Ffriends who they stayed with when they
OL,10,Fcame to Scotland.
OL,12,FBut, in 1985, these friends were
OL,13,Funable to put them up and instead
OL,14,Fasked their neighbours - Shirley's
OL,15,Fparents - if they could accommodate
OL,16,Fthe Welsh rugby fans for a couple of
OL,17,Fnights.
OL,19,FDai, who was one of the fans staying
OL,20,Fwith Shirley's parents, spotted a
OL,21,Fphotograph of her on the mantelpiece.
