OL,7,FWhen Shirley arrived to help out with
OL,8,Fthe guests, Dai asked something
OL,9,Fneither she nor her parents were
OL,10,Fexpecting.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales, she said:
OL,13,F"More or less, the first thing he
OL,14,Fasked me was, 'Have you got anything
OL,15,Fin July, what are you doing in July?'
OL,16,FAnd I said, 'Well, nothing I can think
OL,17,Fof,' and he said 'How would you like
OL,18,Fto marry me?"
