OL,7,F"So, there you go, that is an opening
OL,8,Fline. I went through to the kitchen
OL,9,Fafter a while, telling my parents,
OL,10,F'That daft Welshman through there has
OL,11,Fjust asked me to marry him.'
OL,13,F"Of course, my dad just splurted his
OL,14,Ftea and my mum said, 'Oh my God, what
OL,15,Fa joke.' But it proved to be quite
OL,16,Fserious."
