OL,7,FAfter some months of phone calls,
OL,8,Fletters, and visits, Dai officially
OL,9,Fasked Shirley to marry him on a trip
OL,10,Fto the Isle of Skye. The couple
OL,11,Fselected a ring in Edinburgh on their
OL,12,Fway back to the Scottish Borders.
OL,14,FDai sold the house he owned in Cardiff
OL,15,Fand together they bought a house in
OL,16,FNorthumberland.
OL,18,FWhile Dai had originally asked Shirley
OL,19,Fto marry him in July, the couple
OL,20,Fmarried on the 3rd August 1985 and
OL,21,Fwent on to have three children.
